365
00:24:24,420 --> 00:24:25,570
I understand.

366
00:24:25,570 --> 00:24:29,510
Maybe what I just said has complicated your judgments.

367
00:24:29,510 --> 00:24:32,420
Don't let what I just said sway your decision making.

368
00:24:32,420 --> 00:24:35,400
