409
00:27:29,160 --> 00:27:34,350
I can hear your strategy of going with the flow and counter measure for measure.

410
00:27:34,350 --> 00:27:38,110
But I think it might be better if we strike first to gain the initiative.

411
00:27:38,110 --> 00:27:42,620
It's the perfect timing to get rid of the cancer in the Society.

412
00:27:42,620 --> 00:27:48,460
I heard that your EEG Technology Committee is having an internal voting.

413
00:27:52,250 --> 00:27:54,010
